		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I always felt 5th to 6th is more significant. N64 was nice and PS1 was okay, but there was a huge jump in graphics quality from PS1 and N64 to say PS2 and Xbox etc, that solidified 3D graphics as the future of console gaming. The 5th generation seemed experimental and maybe premature, and though it was a large jump in processing power so was the 6th generation.

		

		</td>
